data.description: Exceptional opportunity to own this updated condo in Dublin Schools. Inviting front porch leads into a light & bright open floor plan.. Kitchen offers SS appl's, granite countertops, wine rack, gas range, new faucet, under cabinet lighting and open to the family room w/gas fireplace. New ceiling fans.. LVP flooringthroughout first floor Enjoy sitting on the rebuilt deck (2 years old) with a gorgeous water/fountain view. Finished lower level is finished w/1/2 bath and storage area. Oversized 2 car garage. HVAC(2 years old). Brand new windows being installed, Nest thermostat and smart outdoor lighting. Better hurry!
